    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of Bavarian engineering, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. Power is delivered through a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a variable M-differential lock. The chassis remains taut with factory-spec bushings and a reinforced subframe, while the Double-VANOS system has been precision-calibrated for optimal valve timing. Finished in Carbon Black over Nappa leather, the exterior retains its factory depth with zero paint correction required. Mechanically flawless and aesthetically concours-ready, this is a true turn-key investment for the discerning driver.",
